# ===================================================
# MPL Website 2 — Monorepo Root .env.example
# ===================================================
# This file documents environment variables for the
# entire monorepo. Each package also has its own
# .env.example with package-specific variables.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in real values — never commit .env files!
#   3. For the web app, also copy apps/web/.env.example
# ===================================================

# (No monorepo-level variables required at this time.
#  All runtime config lives in apps/web/.env.example)
